snippet.title: Nemesis: Distress - Official Early Access Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Nemesis: Distress, is the first-person multiplayer shooter in which everyone's not exactly sure who's to blame aboard a spaceship on which you are not alone... Nemesis: Distress is based on the popular board game and will be released into Early Access on Steam on June 16.

#IGN #Gaming
